videos.description: Kerryon Johnson returns from his injury with a one-yard touchdown run on Auburn's first drive.
videos.headline: Johnson waltz's into the end zone for TD

videos.headline: Lock picked off by Auburn's Davis

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson scores his second touchdown of the quarter from the wildcat formation.

videos.description: Kerryon Johnson runs it in from 1-yard out for his third rushing touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Johnson scores 3rd TD of the half

videos.headline: Deja Vu?  Johnson scores 4th TD of the half

videos.headline: Johnson scores 5th rushing TD

videos.headline: Lock hits Moore for 2nd TD pass

videos.headline: Johnson and Auburn too much for Missouri
